                <note rend="inline" type="source">740.00112 European War 1939/4927: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Acting Secretary of State</gloss> to
                        the Chargé at Tangier</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Childs</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1942-03-28T16:00:00-04:00"
                            >March 28, 1942—4 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>55. Your 116, March 13. If possible, please postpone your dinner for subject
                    pending receipt of letter which Department is sending you by quickest available
                    means.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Welles</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
